{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "shopapi-collection-v1",
    "name": "ShopAPI",
    "description": "Complete ShopAPI collection.\n\n**Quick Start:**\n1. Make sure the API is running on https://localhost:5001\n2. Use `Auth / Login as Admin` or `Auth / Login as Customer` — the token is saved automatically\n3. All protected requests use `{{token}}` automatically — no manual copy-paste needed\n\n**Seeded Accounts:**\n- Admin: admin@shop.com / Admin123!\n- Customer: john@customer.com / Customer123!\n- Customer: jane@customer.com / Customer123!\n\n**Role Rules:**\n- Customers → can browse products and manage their own orders\n- Admin → full access to everything",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl",  "value": "https://localhost:2858", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "token",    "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "customerId", "value": "1", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "productId",  "value": "1", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "orderId",    "value": "1", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "item": [

    {
      "name": "🔐 Auth",
      "item": [

        {
          "name": "Register",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status is 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('Success is true', () => {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(json.success).to.be.true;",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"newuser\",\n  \"email\": \"newuser@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Password123!\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","auth","register"] },
            "description": "Register a new user. All new accounts are created with the **Customer** role."
          }
        },

        {
          "name": "Login as Admin 🔑",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status is 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('Has token', () => pm.expect(json.data.token).to.be.a('string').and.not.empty);",
                  "pm.test('Role is Admin', () => pm.expect(json.data.role).to.eql('Admin'));",
                  "// Auto-save token for all subsequent requests",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.data.token);",
                  "console.log('✅ Admin token saved:', json.data.token.substring(0,40) + '...');"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@shop.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Admin123!\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","auth","login"] },
            "description": "Login as Admin. Token is **automatically saved** to `{{token}}` and used by all protected requests."
          }
        },

